@node About " About FAMEStyle v4.o"

@{b}                                Ě
@{ub}   (c) Mogue! / Desaster '98  @{b} /_   @{ub}    (Desaster! FAMEProductions 1998)
@{b}@{fg highlight}       - ------------------ -@{fg text}__ / ____@{b}@{fg highlight} - ------------------------------ -
@{ub}@{fg text}         FAMEStyle v4.o      @{b}\\///\\\\  /  @{ub}@{fg highlight}[@{fg text}o1/o6 - About FAMEStyle      @{fg highlight}]
@{b}@{fg highlight} - -@{fg text}/@{b}@{fg highlight}------------------ - @{fg text}    /_»» \\//\\ @{b}@{fg highlight}- ------------------------------ -@{fg text}
                               /     »»
                              Ě

@{ub}@{fg text} Time passed by since the last FAMEStyle issue, this time we present you
 the fourth issue of the never ending FAMEStyle serie.
 As usually this archive is filled with lottsa logos in ansi and ascii
 format to use with your bulletin board system.
 Take a look at the content list below to know what logos we've included
 this time.

 If you're interested in getting a logo for your BBS, group or just your
 handle note that there is currently only one way to get it, try to
 catch Tolpan of Desaster in IRC at the channels #AmiElite or #TRSI-FAME
 and let him know about.

@endnode

