@{ub}@{fg text}         FAMEStyle v4.o      @{b}\\///\\\\  /  @{ub}@{fg highlight}[@{fg text}o5/o6 - The installation (?) @{fg highlight}]
@{b}@{fg highlight} - -@{fg text}/@{b}@{fg highlight}------------------ - @{fg text}    /_»» \\//\\ @{b}@{fg highlight}- ------------------------------ -@{fg text}
                               /     »»
                              Ě

@{ub}@{fg text} Well, teher isn't much to say about just copy the files/directories
 anywhere you like (eG: FAME:Screens/) and rename the files inside or edit
 your Bull(x).Txt files.

 That's it!.

@endnode
