@{b}@{fg highlight} - -@{fg text}/@{b}@{fg highlight}------------------ - @{fg text}    /_»» \\//\\ @{b}@{fg highlight}- ------------------------------ -@{fg text}
                               /     »»
                              Ě

@{ub}@{fg text} The best way to get in toch with us is by calling one of our bulletin
 board systems.
 Our homepage is (as usally) still in progress and it's currently imposible
 to reach me via email/inet, within the next release i'll fix a new email add
 and inet account as soon as possible.

 To catch Gravedancer send your email to: Gravedancer@PoBoxes.Com
 To catch Tolpan send your email to: Tolpan@Skom.Rhein.De or check out
 #TRSI-FAME.
